U.K. Stocks Drop; Benchmark FTSE 100 Index Declines 0.6 Percent in London

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-12-07T13:28:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/u-k-stocks-drop-benchmark-ftse-100-index-declines-0-6-percent-in-london.html
U.K. stocks declined, reversing
earlier gains. The benchmark FTSE 100 Index lost 35.77, or 0.6
percent, to 5,532.95 as of 1:29 p.m. in  London . The gauge
earlier rallied as much as 1.1 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
